These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: cauliflower, garlic, lettuce, pumpkin, radish
The people use 5 different means of transport: tram, boat, subway, jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
3. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the subway##2
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
8. the person eating pumpkin is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | garlic | cauliflower | radish | pumpkin | lettuce |
| Transport   | subway  | snowmobile      | jet-ski   | tram     | boat    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea, tea, water
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, pomegranate, cucumber, grapes, broccoli
1. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
3. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
4. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
5. the person eating nectarine is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating grapes##2
6. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | tea       | water    | almond-milk | fanta   |
| Food      | pomegranate | nectarine | grapes | broccoli      | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, game, siglo, old-henry, blend
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, electronic, metal, reggae, trance
1. the fan of reggae is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4
3. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of metal##1
4. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
5. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
6. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
7. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
8. the blend-smoker is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Cigar         | davidoff | siglo | game | old-henry    | blend |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | blues        | metal      | electronic | trance      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, august, may, march, october
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, martial-arts, satire, scientific, spy
1. the person who's birthday is in may is in the middle##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
6. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person watching satire movies and the person who's birthday is in october##2
7. the person watching spy movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Birthday         | april      | march | may | august   | october  |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | spy    | satire        | adventure | martial-arts |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, rock-climbing, singing, card-games
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, brazilian, canadian, egyptian, japanese
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the australian##1
3. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left of the japanese##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3
5. the japanese is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the egyptian##1
7. the brazilian is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby      | card-games      | magic-tricks | fishing   | singing  | rock-climbing  |
| Nationality   | canadian | egyptian | australian | brazilian | japanese |

