.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, lemonade, mirinda, tea
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, hedgehog, frog, turtle
1. the person drinking cola is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the turtle and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | cola        | 7up                | mirinda  | lemonade  | tea            |
| Pet        | chinchilla | turtle | lizard | hedgehog | frog |

