.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, july, january, june, september
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, electrician, firefighter, librarian, paramedic
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the electrician##3
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the electrician##3
3. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
5. the firefighter is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
7. the doctor is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
8. the paramedic is on the right of the electrician##1
9. the librarian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Birthday   | september       | january   | july    | june    | march |
| Job        | firefighter | doctor | electrician | paramedic | librarian     |

