.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: chinese, egyptian, indian, indonesian, thai
5 different games are played: go, scrabble, billiard, canasta, bridge
1. the person playing go is in an even position##4
2. the indonesian is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is the indonesian##1
4. the indonesian is on the far right##1
5. the egyptian is the person playing go##1
6. the indian is between the egyptian and the chinese##2
7. the person playing bridge is on the right of the indian##1
8. the person playing scrabble is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | thai | egyptian | indian     | chinese | indonesian |
| Game           | scrabble | go     | billiard | bridge    | canasta      |

