There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, water, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person drinking milk is the accountant##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an odd position##4
6. the lawyer is on the left of the dancer##1
7. the firefighter is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | lawyer | dancer | firefighter | accountant | analyst |
| Beverage   | water | hot-chocolate | soy-milk    | milk    | almond-milk  |

