.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There 5 different types of food: broccoli, garlic, pepper, radish, spinach
House: victorian, modern, cape-cod, craftsman, gothic-revival
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the craftsman house##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the modern house##3
3. the person eating broccoli is between the cape-cod house and the modern house##2
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
5. the gothic-revival house is the person eating pepper##1
6. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating garlic is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | garlic    | spinach  | broccoli      | radish     | pepper |
| House   | victorian | modern | craftsman | cape-cod | gothic-revival |

