.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-13::.
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, fish, dog, ferret, lizard
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, spanish
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4
2. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
3. the pakistani is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the fish is between the australian and the owner of the dog##2
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the mexican##3
8. the australian is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Pet      | lizard       | dog | fish | ferret   | goldfish   |
| Nationality   | pakistani | mexican | spanish  | australian | nigerian |

