.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, december, july, november, february
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, chess, dancing, traveling, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Birthday    | february   | november  | december     | september | july |
| Hobby   | board-games | dancing | woodworking | traveling | chess      |

