.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, yellow, mauve, black, azure
There are 5 different nationalities: american, british, chinese, colombian, turkish
1. the american is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
2. the person who likes grey is on the left or right of the colombian##3
3. the american is on the left of the chinese##1
4. the chinese is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
5. the british is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
6. the person who likes mauve is on the left or right of the person who likes yellow##3
7. the chinese is in an odd position##4
8. the colombian is in the middle##1
9. the british is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Color   | yellow  | mauve    | black | grey   | azure |
| Nationality   | turkish | british | colombian    | american | chinese |

