.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: gospel, house, jazz, metal, pop
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, video-games, cooking, puzzles, hiking
1. the fan of metal is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of pop is between the fan of house and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
6. the fan of house is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | metal | jazz     | pop     | house |
| Hobby     | puzzles   | video-games   | sudoku | cooking | hiking  |

