.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, card-games, cooking, photography, reading
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, coral, azure, grey, yellow
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who likes azure is the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes grey is on the far left##1
4. the person who likes white is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
5. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is baking and the person who likes yellow##2
6. the person who likes coral is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who likes yellow##2
7. the person who likes grey is in an odd position##4
8. the person who likes yellow is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Hobby         | photography | cooking | card-games | reading | baking     |
| Color   | grey    | coral   | yellow       | azure | white |

