.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  software-developer, firefighter, doctor, dancer, librarian
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, quad-bike, snowmobile, taxi, train
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the train and the person driving the taxi##2
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the librarian##1
5. the dancer is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is the software-developer##1
7. the firefighter is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Job   | software-developer | doctor      | dancer | librarian     | firefighter      |
| Transport     | train | quad-bike | taxi | airplane | snowmobile |

 